snippet.title: Shaun White Skateboarding - Launch Trailer [Europe]
snippet.description:
More info on http://www.shaunwhitegame.com.
CHANGE STREETS INTO HALF-PIPES, and extend rails for endless grinds, alone or with friends, in the only game that gives you the POWER TO SHAPE, CREATE, AND RIDE THE ULTIMATE SKATEPARK. 

Shaun White Skateboarding -- AVAILABLE OCTOBER 28TH.
